content: This is a good looking watch face! I got it and am enjoying it as my new "daily driver".

This isn't a reflection of the app/watch face itself, but when trying to install, I paid the $1.50 in the play store on my phone, but then my watch wanted another $1.50 to install there... Nope. Developer has been great and is looking into the issue. Hope to be able to update my review again if sorted out.
replyContent:
Hi Brendan,

this is a common Google Play bug. It takes Google some time to update the purchase status for all of your devices and stores. Normally you should be able to download the watch face after around 15 minutes.

Best Regards

I am very pleased that you like the watchface.
